### Get all users
GET http://localhost:5064/api/users
Accept: application/json

###

### Get user by ID
GET http://localhost:5064/api/users/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Add a new user
POST http://localhost:5064/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Johnson",
  "email": "alice.johnson@techhive.com",
  "department": "HR"
}

###

### Update an existing user
PUT http://localhost:5064/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "alice.smith@techhive.com",
  "department": "IT"
}

###

### Delete a user
DELETE http://localhost:5064/api/users/1